Hey guys! sorry i havent been on in a couple days.. im in houston. but im coming back tommorow.

im up here visiting grandparents.. and for father's day.. and seeing my grandpa..

he has like three different kinds of cancer.. i don't know which ones.. i just hear my mom talking about it that its in his bones and kidneys or somehting like that.. i dont ask to many questions cuz i dont really want to know all the answers.. you know.. its just hard on me.. as it would be if anyone you loved were dying..  and like we dont know how long he might have.. the doctors say a "month" OR "months".. whatever. i really look up to him.. he's so strong.. he looks like hes perfect.. and could go run a mile or something.. but i know that's not the case. well i just gotta look on the brightside.. you no how that goes..

ive been having to do that a lot lately.. hmm..

well im coming home tommorow!

so talk and see all yal when i'm home..

                                     Love,  Leah!
